            "title": "鴻海擬增持鴻華先進1.2萬張持股 深化電動車長期布局",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8kVTVaX8W2EuruT3bd.csw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/4945a050528a1ba6cc8f80d46bdf3bac\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
